# Conversation Logging Protocol

## CRITICAL: Mandatory Logging
Create/update conversation log AFTER EVERY TURN with any action.

## CRITICAL: Active Work Tracking
Review and update `.project_management/active_work_tracking.org` every session:
- At start: Review objectives
- During work: Update progress
- At end: Mark completed tasks

## Log Location
- Directory: `.project_management/conversation_logs/[code-name]/`
- Filename: `[YYYY-MM-DD]_session_log.org`

## Required Log Content
### Header
```org
#+TITLE: Conversation Log - [Code Name]
#+DATE: [YYYY-MM-DD]
#+MODEL: [Code Name]
#+SESSION_START: [timestamp]
#+FILETAGS: :conversation:log:[code-name]:
```

### Sections
- **Discussion Summary**: Topics, decisions, requests
- **Changes Made**: Files modified/created/deleted with line numbers
- **Rationale**: Why changes were made
- **Cross-References**: Links to cleanup reports, architecture updates

## Format
```org
* Turn [N]: [Brief Description]
  :PROPERTIES:
  :TIMESTAMP: [HH:MM:SS]
  :END:

** Discussion Summary
** Changes Made
** Rationale
** Next Steps Identified
```

